<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />The worthless person is despised in his eyes,</para>

<para style="q1">but he honors those who fear Yahweh.</para>

<para style="q1">He swears to his own disadvantage and does not take back his promises.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />He does not charge interest when he lends money.</para>

<para style="q1">He does not take bribes to testify against the innocent.</para>

<para style="q1">He who does these things will never be shaken.</para>
